{"tid":1835089,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(癲撚左) 公安抓造謠者，抓他原因是把死亡人數報少了","createTime":"2020-01-22T16:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T05:11:32.000Z","uid":222970,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea850cc8e75364693e8f5c52da14c22915c7594","tid":1835089,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"公安抓造謠者，事後稱抓他的原因是把死亡人數報少了<br />\n<br />\n1/4 山東鄆城，最先爆料的是一名網友，他說有9人死亡，隨後被拘留，理由是造謠。隨著媒體不斷介入，真相逐漸被扒開，一個多星期後，官方通報承認了此事故，死亡21人。<br />\n面對媒體的指責，官方說拘留他是因為他把人數說少了。<br />\nWTF？隨便吧，你們開心就好 <br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n品蔥<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/h4q765j0bA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fh4q765j0bA&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzN9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=a5b06a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/h4q765j0bA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dy5sRkV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDy5sRkV.jpg&h=2b1e7cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2/4 再來對比第二個案例，山東壽光洪災，官方先是（已經到達挺嚴重的程度）宣稱零死亡，並拘留了多名&ldquo;誇大災情&rdquo;的造謠者。後來，事情逐漸蓋不住，承認了有死亡，並且倒塌房屋9999間（按規定，如果倒塌一萬間就需要啟動4級應急預案）。那為啥造謠0死亡的官員不拘留？面對這個指責，有村官跪地道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P39M6Ut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP39M6Ut.jpg&h=2968cff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3/4武漢肺炎，官方第一時間拘捕了8名造謠者。至於他們說了什麼，到底是不是造謠，我也不清楚，但是叼盤俠胡錫進都替他們說話了，那他們勢必很冤。<br />\n<br />\n我不知道，一個人智商要低到什麼程度，才能看不出來官方其實不在意什麼謠不謠，他只在意這個消息對他有利還是有害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FE7byzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFE7byzy.jpg&h=f8a0b7f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4/4 而為什麼說官方最在意的是消息是否對他們有利？<br />\n換成你，你也一樣。如果你有不受約束的權力可以掌控輿論，那麼你首先想要消除自然是對你不利的聲音，而謠言？如果與你利益沒有牽扯，那整治一下也無妨。<br />\n可以說後來被感染的病人都是輿論管控的受害者，畢竟：<br />\nTruth doesn&rsquo;t kill, ignorance does."},{"pid":"ec9ba83ea91b30daff997ee70fcae55f07ff55d4","tid":1835089,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"支那logic <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173aa71d3a4dc1c671180ef9c8b0c081146f295c","tid":1835089,"uid":266100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8af9fd6536f82589d2c746064426766bb335da78","tid":1835089,"uid":291626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"正常發揮"},{"pid":"da0e61b481514e7ae12546bce4ddd5ebdd4ace61","tid":1835089,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c8297fbec2c45fce5b11c60df078bd192f008d","tid":1835089,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦，鬼叫佢出世喺鬼國，仲要估數字估唔中咩"},{"pid":"6212907633e864d4b6042ba43d7ddb3e30d1e8a1","tid":1835089,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffe9702df312052e67eb248f7f04beb973f54b3","tid":1835089,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:39:01.000Z","msg":"計埋佢咪慢慢湊返條數"},{"pid":"25a6e624d8f88ea44058fa1c4eab3edb86c4bb29","tid":1835089,"uid":215270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"唔撚出聲就唔會講錯 咁就一定冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafc124d997b6717dff64e4ee0edd02cb302d7ab","tid":1835089,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj